features: 【LIFT-TOP Design】The tabletop can be lifted and closed effortlessly, creating a versatile work surface. It is not only a functional coffee table in the living room or reception room, but also a home office desk while you don't need to lean forward.

【Spacious Storage】This minimalist coffee table is designed with a hidden compartment and an open shelf for different storage needs. Laptops, gamepads, blankets and pillows can be hidden under the raiseable tabletop. The bottom shelf is spacious and stable to hold storage boxes, room decorations and other displays.

【Soft-close Mechanism】The high-quality metal rod with buffer provides stable support for the lifting desktop. Lids will go down slowly and gently to avoid slams shut and crush the little fingers of children, providing customers with a good user experience and safety guarantee.
【Sturdy & Durable】The strong and water-resistant MDF wood board ensure stability and durability for years of use. Ideal for working, dining in the living room.

【Quality Warranty】Comes with the coffee table with our assembly instructions, you can easily assemble it in a short time. Any question before and after purchase, please contact us and we will find solution for you in 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars What a great table
reviews.reviewText: This thing is great. It works great for eating dinner at the couch and using a mouse and keyboard if you have a pc hooked up to your TV.I don’t know about the other reviews saying this was difficult to put together, I would say they are clearly wrong. The instructions are super clear and the only reason I could see someone struggling is if they have never successfully put together any furniture in their life. It’s a very simple and straightforward design.If put together correctly and making sure all the nuts and bolts are tight, this table feels very sturdy. I would recommend this table to anyone who is looking for something of this nature.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice design, sturdy and perfect fit
reviews.reviewText: Love this coffee table. Instructions were easy to follow. Lots of storage space, easy to move nice color. Wish I had purchased this several years ago.It's recommended to have 2 people to assemble this, however, I was able to put ot together myself in about 45 minutes I did get the top lid backwards and had to remove that one and turn it around. Thats the part where 2 people would have really helped, but i was finally able to get it righted, so double check the fit before you tighten all the screws.Two tools are provided. Wrench and small Phillips screwdriver. If you have access to an electric screwdriver, definitely use that one.The top lid/cover seems like it could hold a decent weight (1/2" solid wood) The inner shelf (flimsy board like material <1/4" )shouldn't be used for heavier items though.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars EXTREMELY HARD TO PUT TOGETHER
reviews.reviewText: The finished product looks great but it is not sturdy. Also, I would not have anything on top when you raise it for fear of collapsing. Nice decorative piece but not sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It is a little difficult to build but it is totally worth it

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Flimsy and Difficult to Assemble Alone
reviews.reviewText: I had to get a replacement since the first I ordered came damaged.The second one seemed in better shape.The instructions recommend 2 people do this, I agree with the suggestion. Of course, not everyone has another person to do this with.I assembled it alone to the best of my ability, followed the instructions, and the table isn’t very sturdy. It wobbles a bit side to side and I tried fixing this before moving forward to the next steps and nothing made it more secure.I’m thinking maybe some wood glue where there’s some gaps may help, but I haven’t done so yet.On the plus side they sent 4 extra of each tool I’d need.It’s a nice looking table, and the lift is great. However, save your money and get something sturdier and invite a friend or get help with assembly for sure if you do get this table.Update: it broke. Lol

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Had no problem putting it together. Im a Senior Female and had no problems. Perfect for small space. Very sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Price is right
reviews.reviewText: Make no mistake, you get what you pay for… but we’re very happy with this table. The materials are very cheap, so we bought a twelve pack of cork coasters and we use them religiously for all drinks. The lift top feature has been used way more than we thought we would! Great height for working on the laptop or eating snacks in front of tv. Overall a great table I would recommend, take care of it and it’ll take care of you!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Nice color, the lid opens and closes as expected.Some scratches and marks on parts due to packaging. I was disappointed, but figured whatever! Wasn’t going to deal with retuning it.It serves it purpose. I was able to assemble alone, I’m good at this stuff.
